claim.claim-text:
9. A method for transmitting information on position information identifier to a receiving device including at least one of a data base of position information identifiers and a database of a digital map, said method comprising the steps of; 
transmitting information on said position information identifier and coordinate row information to said receiving device; and 
executing a map matching process at said receiving device in order to determine a position on said digital map; 
wherein said coordinate row information includes nodes and interpolating points, both of which are constituting said position information identifier, and 
wherein said determined position on said digital map corresponds to said position information identifier.
